snippet.title: Towers of Thana - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Towers of Thana is a hero-centric strategy game where you defend mythologies against a dark corruption that wants to swallow them whole. Travel to their homelands and rally legendary gods and creatures to your cause against Ogur, a God turned evil, and his corruption. Releasing in Summer 2023.

Learn more: https://towersofthana.com
